From: Laurent Pinchart <laurent.pinchart+renesas@ideasonboard.com>

The MAX9286 deserializes video data received on up to 4 Gigabit
Multimedia Serial Links (GMSL) and outputs them on a CSI-2 port using up
to 4 data lanes.

